\par My father once told me that respect for the truth comes close to being the basis for all morality. \'93Something cannot emerge from nothing,\'94 he said. This is profound thinking if you understand how unstable \'93the truth\'94 can be.
\par -from \'93Conversations with Muad'Dib\'94 by the Princess Irulan
